    "Of a total of 20 participants (Table 1), 10 were female (50%) and 10 were male (50%), spanning three different levels of degree (seven Bachelor students, eight Master students, five Doctorate students).",
    "Their IELTS scores ranged from a score of 5 to 7.5.",
    "Participants were also evenly divided into high and low AI literacy categorizations.",
